  "texts": [
    "For instance, a finetuned version of GPT, such as ChatGPT, can be repurposed for tasks like text classification and NER, often with a high level of accuracy (Raiaan et al., 2024).",
    "This is achieved through techniques like zero-shot or few-shot prompting, enabling the model to apply its learned language understanding to new tasks with minimal additional training (Barbhuiya et al., 2024; Raiaan et al., 2024).",
    "This adaptability highlights the potential of LLMs to address a variety of challenges across different domains, making them invaluable tools in natural language processing and beyond.",
    "The versatility of LLMs in processing word sequences applies to various types of sequential biological data (Sarumi and Heider, 2024).",
    "Both BERT and GPT models have been adapted for genomic, proteomic, and gene expression analyses (Rehana et al., 2023 (Rehana et al.,, 2024;; Sarumi and Heider, 2024)."
